*.log
*.pem
# Re-include library CA bundles (e.g. certifi cacert.pem) required for TLS at
# runtime; without this the *.pem rule strips certifi.where()'s cacert.pem from
# the FC package and the controller crashes at boot on ssl.load_verify_locations.
# The *.pem rule above still excludes any stray secret .pem outside python/.
!python/**/*.pem
!python/certifi/cacert.pem
*.key
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
docs/**
tests/**
design-system/**
scripts/**
deploy/**
AGENTS.md
PROMPTS.md
codex-config.snippet.toml
